.TH PRT-SYNC 8 "prt-#VERSION# Manual"
.SH NAME
prt-sync \- Synchronize ports collection
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prt sync
.SH DESCRIPTION
Connects to one or more master repositories and updates the local copy
of a ports collection.
.br
A port is a directory containing all necessary files for building a
software package using pkgmk(8).
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /usr/ports/
Root of local ports collection.
.TP
.I /etc/ports/
Directory for port collection configuration.
.TP
.I /etc/ports/drivers/
Directory for driver scripts.
